<strong>Studio Album, released in 1987</strong><br><br>

<strong>Songs / Tracks Listing</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">1. Sand (5:25) <br>2. Distance Vs. Desire (5:17) <br>3. Pud Wud (6:43) <br>4. Clown (5:14) <br>5. The 4.15 Bradford Executive (8:28) <br>6. Mac Man (4:02)<br><br>Total Time: 35:06</p>

<strong>Line-up / Musicians</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">- Allan Holdsworth / SynthAxe, guitar (3), producer<br><br>With:<br>- Alan Pasqua / keyboards (3)<br>- John England / Mac computer programming (6)<br>- Jimmy Johnson / bass<br>- Biff Vincent / Octopad bass (6)<br>- Gary Husband / drums (1,3)<br>- Chad Wackerman / drums (4,5), percussion (6)</p>

<strong>Releases information</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">
LP Relativity &#8206;- 88561-8152-1 (1987, US)<br><br>CD Relativity &#8206;- 88561-8152-2 (1987, US)<br>CD CREAM Records &#8206;- CR2902 (2009, UK) Remastered by Tohru Ohara<br>
